David C. Arch  Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, Blistex Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 40 Board Members in 40 different organizations across 42 different industries.See Board Relationships72--
Background

		Mr. David C. Arch serves as the Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer at Blistex Inc. Mr. Arch has been a Managing General Partner at Van Kampen Exchange Fund since 1998. He serves as a Managing General Partner of funds in the Van Kampen Fund Complex. He serves as an Independent Trustee or Director of various funds in the Invesco/Van Kampen fund complex/AIM fund complex. He served as a Director of Morgan Stanley Institutional Fund, Inc. - Opportunity Portfolio ... since 2003. He served as a Director or Trustee of investment companies in Van Kampen Funds complex from 1984 to 2010. He served as a Trustee at Elmhurst Memorial Healthcare Inc. He serves as a Member of Board of Visitors, Institute for the Humanities at University of Michigan. He is a Director of St. Vincent de Paul Center and Illinois Manufacturers' Association. Mr. Arch is a Member of the World President Organization-Chicago Chapter and Heartland Alliance.Read Full Background




